## ğŸ“¦ What is a Variable?

A **variable** is like a labeled box where you store something.

Imagine you have a box, you put a label that says "toys", and inside you store your favorite toys.

```elixir
# Creating a variable is like putting something in a box
name = "Mary"
age = 9
favorite_color = "blue"

IO.puts(name)
IO.puts(age)
IO.puts(favorite_color)
```

## ğŸ¨ Using Variables in Messages

```elixir
name = "Peter"
age = 8

IO.puts("Hello, my name is #{name}")
IO.puts("I am #{age} years old")
IO.puts("In one year I will be #{age + 1} years old")
```

